# Generation Instructions for guides/code-review-guidelines.md

## Context

You are generating the code review guidelines — project-specific standards for how reviews are conducted.

This file covers the **human process** (how to review, how to respond, severity levels). Technical review rules (what to check for security, performance, architecture, etc.) live in separate competency files under `workflows/review/`. Do NOT duplicate those rules here.

**Audience**: All developers (reviewers and code authors)
**Tone**: Professional, constructive
**Length**: 200-300 lines

